# pyenv
#   For a library or package, you might want to share your Python version
#   .python-version

# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if delegates have different OS, they may change the lockfile.
#   Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipenv, True or False depends on circumstances
#   poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipenv, True or False depends on circumstances
#   pdm.lock
#   .pdm-plugins/

